<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>173</hymn_number>
<author>Thangngur</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Nawpna zing Aksi Lalpa,
 Bitna suongpi Lal Isu;
 Entie, Mihiem chate hih,
 Khawvel kipahna hawlin;
 Manthaina mun a zuon ui,
 Amau ah Nang na dingin

[V2]
 Na mel a kipahna kim,
 Nang ngei neiha muonna chu;
 Mi cheng chengin hun heu henla hileh,
 Kuon gitloh na a hawl dem?
 A manthaina ding mai un.

[V3]
 2. Thihna gu natzie mi gen,
 Gitloh huoisiet zie mi gen;
 A hihziekin Lal Isu,
 Gen liengthei keihaw ziekin;
 Ling lukhuk leh than khuk thim,
 Kalvari chanin Na hung,

[V4]
 3. A thukzie leh a san zie,
 A sauzie a letzie chu,
 Lei leh vana thil tincheng,
 Gi hawih leh pautin chengin
 Na hehpihna lopi hi,
 Kipakin phuongzak u hen.

[V5]
 4. Ka lunggil Temple sungah,
 Mun sangpen hi chang leh chin,
 Lopina lopi chunga
 Nawpna chunga van nawpna.
 Keihaw a hung hitana,
 Ziechuh Nang ngei chu Na hi.</lyrics>
<title>Nawpna Zing Aksi!</title>
</song>